{
  "stem": "19218.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But while going there, I had a sack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I found some carrots on the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I found some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I didn't think-- I guess the mind wasn't working straight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That is, couldn't be it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I put everything in my sack because I'm going to be hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I ate a carrot, a potato.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It didn't matter whether it was cooked or raw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, it was something to eat, a carrot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I kept on accumulating the things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, we came into a home, and we were-- we were-- we had some food immediately.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I remember one particular home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That particular home, the basement had a lot of sausage in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we were eating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were so starved that that night when we went to sleep, we have taken-- put a bench in front of our bed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Put food out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Every time we opened our eyes, or we just awaken, we would grab something and eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And not only this, but even if we had to go to the bathroom, we were eating and sitting [INAUDIBLE] at the same time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, this is how hungry we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Unfortunately, many, many, many of the prisoners, of the-- of the survivors have died after the war, by eating.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "As I said, God still watched over me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I-- I-- I-- I-- I-- must have chosen me to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I've done fine with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Even in one incident, I remember that there was a Jewish chaplain or someone, who found out that we were already liberated, found out we are former concentration camp inmates.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he brought us a jar of peanut butter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Now, we didn't know what peanut butter is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we designated my brother to be the cook for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
